  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>4 PLAYER COOP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Teamwork is essential to complete the challenges</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408210/extras/823b260648982eeb468b9f1242070588.poster.avif?t=1766588305\" width=600 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408210/extras/823b260648982eeb468b9f1242070588.webm?t=1766588305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408210/extras/823b260648982eeb468b9f1242070588.mp4?t=1766588305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHALLENGING TRIALS, PUZZLES, PARKOURS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>While inside the trials you can adjust everything from lightining, duration and visibility to enemy behaviour and difficulty</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408210/extras/34806b635e528ee846b2ee287f2d3305.poster.avif?t=1766588305\" width=600 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408210/extras/34806b635e528ee846b2ee287f2d3305.webm?t=1766588305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408210/extras/34806b635e528ee846b2ee287f2d3305.mp4?t=1766588305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>SINGLE-PLAYER CAMPAIGN</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A representative solo version of the multiplayer      experience</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.a